<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='290000' id='t-290000'>Not usable for a YouTube video.</span>
</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
 5:03
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='292000' id='t-292000'>What we have done</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='294000' id='t-294000'>is we have developed a technology</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='297000' id='t-297000'>with which we can furthermore</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='300000' id='t-300000'>replace the remote control of our light bulb.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='302000' id='t-302000'>We transmit with our technology,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='304000' id='t-304000'>not only a single data stream,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='306000' id='t-306000'>we transmit thousands of data streams</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='308000' id='t-308000'>in parallel,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='310000' id='t-310000'>at even higher speeds.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='312000' id='t-312000'>And the technology we have developed --</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='314000' id='t-314000'>it's called SIM OFDM.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='316000' id='t-316000'>And it's spacial modulation --</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='318000' id='t-318000'>these are the only technical terms, I'm not going into details --</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='321000' id='t-321000'>but this is how we enabled</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='323000' id='t-323000'>that light source</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='325000' id='t-325000'>to transmit data.</span>
</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
 5:39
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='328000' id='t-328000'>You will say, &quot;Okay, this is nice --</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='331000' id='t-331000'>a slide created in 10 minutes.&quot;</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='333000' id='t-333000'>But not only that.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='335000' id='t-335000'>What we've done</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='337000' id='t-337000'>is we have also developed a demonstrator.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='340000' id='t-340000'>And I'm showing for the first time in public</span>
