<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='354000' id='t-354000'>put in our signal processing technology.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='356000' id='t-356000'>And then what we have here is a little hole.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='359000' id='t-359000'>And the light goes through that hole.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='361000' id='t-361000'>There's a receiver.</span>
