<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='404000' id='t-404000'>But at the same time, you see this video coming up here.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='408000' id='t-408000'>And that's a video, a high-definition video</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='411000' id='t-411000'>that is transmitted through that light beam.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='413000' id='t-413000'>You're critical.</span>
