<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='424000' id='t-424000'>(Applause)</span>
</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
 7:20
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='429000' id='t-429000'>Once again.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='432000' id='t-432000'>Still don't believe?</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='435000' id='t-435000'>It is this light</span>
