<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='474000' id='t-474000'>You also have a critical question now, and</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='476000' id='t-476000'>you say, &quot;Okay,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='478000' id='t-478000'>do I have to have the light on all the time</span>
