<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='548000' id='t-548000'>These are potential sources for high-speed data transmission.</span>
</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
 9:23
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='552000' id='t-552000'>And then there's security.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='555000' id='t-555000'>You would agree with me</span>
