<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='582000' id='t-582000'>So the data goes in that direction, not there anymore.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='584000' id='t-584000'>Now we can in fact see where the data is going to.</span>
</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
10:01
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='590000' id='t-590000'>So for me,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='593000' id='t-593000'>the applications of it,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='596000' id='t-596000'>to me, are beyond imagination at the moment.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='600000' id='t-600000'>We have had a century of very nice, smart application developers.</span>
