<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='621000' id='t-621000'>And they use light to illuminate space down there.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='624000' id='t-624000'>And this light can be used to transmit wireless data</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='626000' id='t-626000'>that these things [use] to communicate with each other.</span>
</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
10:40
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='629000' id='t-629000'>Intrinsically safe environments</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='631000' id='t-631000'>like this petrochemical plant --</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='633000' id='t-633000'>you can't use RF, it may generate antenna sparks,</span>
