<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='691000' id='t-691000'>Online life. So that is a vision, I think, that is possible.</span>
</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
11:51
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='700000' id='t-700000'>So, all we would need to do</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='702000' id='t-702000'>is to fit a small microchip</span>
