<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='714000' id='t-714000'>And it's this symbiosis that I personally believe</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='717000' id='t-717000'>could solve the four essential problems</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='719000' id='t-719000'>that face us in wireless communication these days.</span>
